1.Gathering Data
Loading the mnist dataset from the Keras

2.Processing Data
Reshaping the size of the datasets and Normalisation of the vectors

3.Creating Model
Creating Convolution layers and Pooling layers of the CNN, setting the epochs and finally compiling the model

4.Training
Training the model using model.fit () and saving the model

5.Testing
Testing the model with the test datasets

6.Prediction 
Passing the values for the model to predict

7.Graphical User Interface
Loading the model to the GUI and letting the user provide input and the model to predict the output




